OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLord Geidt quits: Boris    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FJohnson's ethics adviser   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fresigns                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The PM's ethics adviser has quit a day 
OL,6, after saying there was a "legitimate   
OL,7, question" about whether Boris Johnson  
OL,8, broke ministerial rules over Partygate.
OL,10,FLord Geidt did not give a reason for   
OL,11,Fleaving the role he took in April, but 
OL,12,Fsaid it was the "right thing" to do.   
OL,14,FHis predecessor, Sir Alex Allan, quit  
OL,15,Fin 2020 after Mr Johnson overruled him 
OL,16,Fover a report into alleged bullying by 
OL,17,FHome Secretary Priti Patel.            
OL,19,FThe government said it was "surprised" 
OL,20,Fby Lord Geidt's decision.              
